{"id":251007,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/奇闻录-戴着红领巾孔庙拜师/","date":"2012-09-10T15:46:54Z","modified":"2012-09-10T15:46:54Z","title":"奇闻录 | 戴着红领巾孔庙拜师","content":"<p><p>2012年9月9日，第三届北京孔庙国子监国学文化节开幕。孔庙大成殿前广场上，孩子们戴着红领巾站在大成殿的汉白玉台阶上，朗朗诵着《弟子规》&#8230;&#8230;<span></span></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/20120910175807.jpg\" title=\" \">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" alt=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/thumbs/thumbs_20120910175807.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/20120910175820.jpg\" title=\" \">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" alt=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/thumbs/thumbs_20120910175820.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/20120910175834.jpg\" title=\" \">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" alt=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/thumbs/thumbs_20120910175834.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/20120910175904.jpg\" title=\" \">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" alt=\"北京国学文化节开幕 百余师生孔庙拜师\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/baishikongzi/thumbs/thumbs_20120910175904.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n</p></div>\n<p>随后，优秀教师代表和中小学生一起走上台，先向孔子行敬师礼，然后由学生向教师行敬师礼，并向老师奉上鲜花和祝福。据悉，文化节持续到9月28日，共有拜师仪式、祭孔大典、御制匾额展览、汉服试穿等12项活动邀请市民参与。</p>\n<p>来源：财新图片</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=rTIcLx1SEhw